string.text: I'm on a mission. Searching some stuff.
Hm. What are you searching? Or maybe you already found something?
Maybe...
Don't hurry! What did you find? I'm searching some stuff too.
I found some documents. Barkeep offered me money for them.
No, nothing. Just some crap.
I see. I thought, maybe you found some documents. I'm here not just for a walk.
Wait! What do you have? Tell me.
That's not your business.
Don't tread on me man.
Need problems? I have 30 of them in my rifle!
Why so serious? I'm just asking.
Oh-oh, very scary! Get out of here!
Well, consider yourself dead!
Why so serious? Let's talk.
Ok, talk. I'm asking again - did you find something?
Documents... I see. I'm here for that documents.\nAnd now you'll give them to me and run away.\nDo you understand?
I understand. Did you find something by yourself?
Maybe.
What documents did you find?
You can take them. They're not so important.
Common documents. Description of some experiments. The title is "Security report".
Ohh... Look, I need them urgently. Let's trade. I can give you a lot of money.
I don't know... Maybe for 20 grands... \nOr an artifact that can cure from zombie condition. Called «Gold Fish».\nBring it to me and I'll give documents to you. Or just give me money.
I have it. Take it!
Oh! Cool! It's very useful.
Crap... Where I can find one?
I don't care.
Man! Where're my documents?
Just kidding! Take your documents.
It's dark and scary here. Burers and snorks around... Why did I agree for all this?! \nWhy are you here?
Go ahead, stalker.
See you!
I don't like when conversation is interrupted in this way! Give me the documents or you'll stay here forever.
Why should I give the documents to you? Found some by yourself?
I don't like when conversation is interrupted in this way! I'm here for valuable documents.\nIf you found something - give me all you have, or you'll get serious problems.\nIf not - get out of here.
Go f*ck yourself!
Well, found Fish? Need documents? Ok, but now I need to Gold Fishes for them.\nJust kidding. Let's trade.\nOr give me all your documents!
Wow, wow! Take it!
Well, found Fish? Need documents? Ok, but now I need to Gold Fishes for them.\nJust kidding. Let's trade.
Found! Need them! Take it!
Well, found Fish? No? Then go find one!
In process.
ÍWell, found Fish? No? Then go find one!\nOr give me all your documents!
What do you want?
Want something else?
Did you change your mind? Need documents? But now I need 100 grands for them.\nJust kidding. Give me 20 grands and documents are yours.
It's too much.
Well, you know where I am.
Crap... Ok, I really need them. Take it.
Oh! Cool! Now I'm rich, huh.
Did you change your mind? Need documents? But now I need 100 grands for them.\nJust kidding. Give me 20 grands and documents are yours. \nOr give me all your documents.
Did you change your mind? No money - no honey.
Did you change your mind? No money - no honey.\nOr give me all your documents
See you!
Ok.
As you say.
Bye.
Bye.
